npm > node package manager

////////
Step to create package.json
///////
**NodeJs installed in your system(https://nodejs.org/en/)
> Navigate to the folder where you want to create using cmd/terminal
> type npm init -y



////////
Step to install packages
///////
> Navigate to the folder where you want to create using cmd/terminal
> npm i express mongodb body-parser 


C Create  > POST
R Read    > GET
U Update  > PUT
D Delete  > Delete

////Step to Run API///////
> Navigate to the folder where you want to create using cmd/terminal
> node server.js /nodemon server.js

